<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #991b1b 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center; }
    .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; }
    .alert-box { background: #fee2e2; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
    .stats { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .stat-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .stat-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .stat-label { font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; }
    .stat-value { font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; }
    .exceeded { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 700; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 16px 40px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 16px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">‚ùå Quota Exceeded</h1>
    <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 18px;">You've exceeded your <%= @resource_name %> limit</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="alert-box">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #991b1b;">
        <%= @percentage.round %>% Used - Over Quota!
      </h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #7f1d1d; font-size: 16px;">
        You're currently <strong><%= number_with_delimiter(@over_by) %></strong> over your limit on the <strong><%= @account.current_plan.titleize %></strong> plan
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat-row">
        <span class="stat-label">Quota</span>
        <span class="stat-value"><%= number_with_delimiter(@quota) %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-row">
        <span class="stat-label">Currently Used</span>
        <span class="stat-value exceeded"><%= number_with_delimiter(@used) %></span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-row">
        <span class="stat-label">Over Quota By</span>
        <span class="stat-value exceeded">+<%= number_with_delimiter(@over_by) %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #fee2e2; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border: 2px solid #dc2626;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #dc2626;">üö® Immediate Action Required</h3>
      <p style="color: #7f1d1d; margin-bottom: 0;">
        You've exceeded your <%= @resource_name %> quota. To continue using ActiveRabbit's features without interruption,
        <strong>please upgrade your plan immediately</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @upgrade_url %>" class="button">
        üöÄ Upgrade Now to Continue
      </a>
    </div>

    <h3>Why Upgrade?</h3>
    <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 0;">
        <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>Higher Limits:</strong> Get more <%= @resource_name %> capacity</li>
        <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>No Interruptions:</strong> Keep all features running smoothly</li>
        <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>Advanced Features:</strong> Unlock AI summaries, automated PRs, and more</li>
        <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>Priority Support:</strong> Get help when you need it</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Choose Your Plan</h3>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
      <tr style="background: white;">
        <td style="padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Team Plan</strong><br><span style="color: #6b7280;">$29/month</span></td>
        <td style="padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">50K errors, 50 AI summaries, 10 PRs</td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background: #f9fafb;">
        <td style="padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;"><strong>Business Plan</strong><br><span style="color: #6b7280;">$80/month</span></td>
        <td style="padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">50K errors, 100 AI summaries, 20 PRs</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="<%= @upgrade_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: white; padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;">
        View All Plans ‚Üí
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        <strong>ActiveRabbit</strong><br>
        AI-Powered Error Tracking & APM for Rails
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
        Questions? Reply to this email or contact support@activerabbit.ai
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

